      • getMatchingRecords

                                                   String scopeRegex,
                                                   String metricRegex,
                                                   String tagKeyRegex,
                                                   String tagValueRegex,
                                                   int limit)
                                            throws IOException
        Returns the schema records matching the specified criteria. At least one field matching expression must be supplied.
        Parameters:
        namespaceRegex - The regular expression on which to match the name space field. May be null.
        scopeRegex - The regular expression on which to match the scope field. May be null.
        metricRegex - The regular expression on which to match the metric field. May be null.
        tagKeyRegex - The regular expression on which to match the tag key field. May be null.
        tagValueRegex - The regular expression on which to match the tag value field. May be null.
        limit - The maximum number of records to return. Must be a positive non-zero integer.
        Returns:
        The matching schema records.
        Throws:
        IOException - If the server cannot be reached.

      • getMatchingRecordFields

                                            String scopeRegex,
                                            String metricRegex,
                                            String tagKeyRegex,
                                            String tagValueRegex,
                                            DiscoveryService.FieldSelector type,
                                            int limit)
                                     throws IOException
        Returns the schema record fields values matching the specified criteria. At least one field matching expression must be supplied.
        Parameters:
        namespaceRegex - The regular expression on which to match the name space field. May be null.
        scopeRegex - The regular expression on which to match the scope field. May be null.
        metricRegex - The regular expression on which to match the metric field. May be null.
        tagKeyRegex - The regular expression on which to match the tag key field. May be null.
        tagValueRegex - The regular expression on which to match the tag value field. May be null.
        type - The field type to return values for.
        limit - The maximum number of records to return. Must be a positive non-zero integer.
        Returns:
        The matching schema records.
        Throws:
        IOException - If the server cannot be reached.
